        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-150",
        "content": "\"Very well,\" said the prince; and, catching her up in his arms, he sprang with her from the rock.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
